description.heading: My time Soleil
description.text: I started my web developing career at Soleil in the autum of 2020, after finishing my bachelor's degree in web development at Karlstad university. Soleil is a small company that focuses on development in the public sector and municipalities around Sweden. During my time at the company i worked mostly as a web developer for Scania, Malmö city, Försäkringskassan (The Swedish insurence fund) and the Award winning website for Bollnäs municipality.
